{
  "stem": "4361.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, they-- there were Hungarian policemen, Hungarian policewomen who carried out about a body search.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a horrible night at the synagogue, children crying, people on the floor, not knowing why.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why are they liquidating the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody says anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came next morning-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the gendarmes this time, Hungarian gendarmes appear on the scene.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they whip us into a row.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The row starts going towards the train station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time the first row arrives at the train station, there is still this winding row which is still at the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were 4,000 people, as we learned later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What they did, they divided the Sziget Jewry in four transports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were the first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now we come to the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is another painful memory because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we come to the train station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all I can think of is the trains I used to watch from my mother house across the field miles and miles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were plain, level fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And twice a day, there was a train which, in the distance, went by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I heard its, its whistle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as a child, I used to run out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a delightful thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I kept saying that this-- I mean, it's trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to love to listen to the whistle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is going-- what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because now we see about 40-- I don't know whether it was 40 or 20, I really don't know-- but I see, we see a number of cattle trains, open cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are we doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
